</style>可以与下一条规则一起兑换为 1 美元。</li><li>逻辑上等价命题的份额可以相互交换。所以如果情况是<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \iff  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟺</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>然后<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股份可以交换<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股份。这是一条显然必须被称为“等价交换法则”的交易规则。我们只允许在一步中可以被视为等价的交换，但是对于任何可以在任意数量的步骤中证明等价的事物，我们可以简单地进行多次交换以获得我们想要的份额。</li><li>人们如何获得他们正在交易的这些股票？简单的！您可以以 1 美元购买<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股票。您还可以以 0 美元的价格购买<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股票，即它们是免费的。</li><li>我们允许交易者执行合乎逻辑的股份分割操作。这是一个特殊的操作，将在下一节中描述。</li></ul><p>正如温特沃斯所解释的那样，该系统的优点在于，为了将股票赎回您可以证明的主张，您需要向运行市场的人透露您的证明。不一定对其他交易者来说，但无论启用上述规则的市场机制是什么，它都可以看到人们进行的交易中隐含的数学证明。</p><h3>逻辑股份分割</h3><p>数学中的一个常见主题是像这样分割证明：首先我们展示<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，然后我们显示<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这使我们能够证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。使用市场的部分目的是将市场上各个交易者的智慧结合起来，形成比任何单个交易者都更强大的东西。因此，理想情况下，我们希望能够证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，即使一个交易者只能证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>和另一个交易者只能证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。假设证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>有一定的利润：股票的交易价格低于 1 美元（比如 0.6 美元），但如果我们只能证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，我们就可以将它们赎回 1 美元。 Alice 知道如何证明（赎回股份） <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。鲍勃知道如何证明（赎回股票） <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B.</span></span></span></span></span></span>他们怎样才能赚钱？</p><p>逻辑份额分割提供了一种方法。它的工作原理是允许将一对股票交换为另一对不同的股票，从而使赎回股票的可能支付保持不变。这是新的股票交换规则，不可能使用之前描述的任何规则进行等价交易。规则：</p><ul><li>对于任意两个命题<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A, B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，逻辑份额分割允许<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额交换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\lor B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额。这种交换可以朝任一方向进行。</li></ul><p>支出保持不变背后的逻辑如下：考虑命题<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A, B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>有多少是正确的。数字为 0、1 或 2。如果两者都不为真，则每个股票中的股份一文不值，合并后的股份也一文不值。如果其中一个为真，一个为假，则<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\lor B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>股份的总价值为 1 美元，而<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>股份的总价值一文不值。最后，如果两者都成立，那么合并后的每股价值 1 美元。 </p><p><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/lesswrong-2-0/image/upload/f_auto,q_auto/v1/mirroredImages/uDXRxF9tGqGX5bGT4/qtbegbmhgbcely9pzgdi" alt=""></p><p>现在让我们看看 Alice 和 Bob 如何通过结合<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>的证明，通过<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股票赚钱<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span><span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B.</span></span></span></span></span></span>首先，爱丽丝可以证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，免费生产许多股<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。如果您通过从一堆免费<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>股票开始并使用等价交换来证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，那么这是可行的。她以每个 0.2 美元的价格将这些东西卖给鲍勃，纯利润。然后 Bob 购买了<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>的很多股票。这些不是从市场机制购买的，市场机制只出售<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span>或<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>股票，而是在公开市场上购买，在这种情况下，它们的定价为 0.6 美元。给定<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的每一个份额，逻辑份额分割允许将它们交换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A\lor B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A\land B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。后者的股份毫无价值，因为我们知道<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>是真的。但前面的股份相当于<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A \implies  B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.225em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⟹</span></span><span class="mjx-mspace" style="width: 0.278em; height: 0px;"></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>并且由于 Bob 有这方面的证明，因此可以将它们兑换为 1 美元。这为 Bob 带来了 0.2 美元的利润。 Alice 和 Bob 的总利润为 0.4 美元，这正好是<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>股票的 0.6 美元价格与假定<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>拥有证据的情况下其应值 1 美元之间的差额。</p><p> （值得注意的是，逻辑份额分割并不<em>需要</em>完成这项工作。毕竟，Alice 和 Bob 一起拥有<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>的证明，因此他们可以在他们之间来回传递份额，根据需要连接他们的子定理并在不再需要它们后将其删除。逻辑上的份额分割只会让他们每个人都更少了解对方在做什么。就鲍勃所知，爱丽丝可能一直在猜测<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>会被证明是正确的，而不是实际上有证明。而且 Alice 在与 Bob 交易时可能不知道 Bob 试图证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。简而言之：如果<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>可证明这一事实反映在<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>股的低价而不是低价中，那就更好了提供在任意股票上粘贴“ <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\land A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">”</span></span></span></span></span></span>服务的价格。此外，由于市场机制只出售真股或假股，因此除了证明它们之外，在其他命题中构建股票的方法也很重要。）</p><p>逻辑股份分割的一个特例是利用排中律根据各种命题铸造股份。例如，给定 1 美元，我们可以购买<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span>的一股，当我们购买时，我们将免费获得<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>的一股。然后使用等价交换（以及排中律），可以将它们转换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\lor \neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land \neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额，以任意选择命题<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。然后使用逻辑份额分割（这次相反），这些可以转换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额。单独而言，这些股票可能具有任何价值，但我们知道它们的价值总和必须为 1 美元，正是因为这种交易是可能的。罗宾·汉森（Robin Hanson）将在命题中将资金转换为股票的交易称为“分割”（为了避免混淆，我们称之为“铸币”），而相反的交易称为“合并”。通过上述规则集，此类操作可以分解为更基本的组成部分：等价交换（采用排中法则）和逻辑份额分割。</p><h3>计算机辅助</h3><p>从理论上讲，历史上任何理解形式逻辑的数学家都可以经营这种市场。然而，手动进行和验证所有交易将需要大量工作，而且收益相对较小。具有明确定义的 API 的计算机化市场要有用得多。我们应该想象这样一个市场上的大多数交易将由计算机进行。像 Coq 这样的证明语言以及自动定理证明器似乎在这里会被大量使用。此外，完全形式化的严格证明对于数学家来说是劳动密集型的，因此大型语言模型可以提供一种将非正式证明和论证转换为证明系统期望的格式的好方法。一般来说，机器学习在这里可能有许多有趣的应用。</p><h3>普通预测市场的应用</h3><p>虽然之前我们一直在描述数学用例，但我们没有理由不包含与现实世界事件的结果相对应的原子份额。然后这些就可以像数学问题一样进行逻辑组合。例如，如果<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>对应“下一任美国总统将是共和党人”， <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>对应“下一任美国副总统将是民主党人”，则可以使用通常的排除中间份额为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>铸造股票- 铸币技术。虽然<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A 股</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>股的交易价格可能处于中等水平，但<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>股的交易价格非常低，这告诉我们<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>对应的事件不是独立的。</p><p>普通的预测市场处理单个事件，但允许事件的逻辑组合没有额外成本。只要我们能够解决每个预测的结果，就可以告诉我们如何解决所有逻辑组合。这是我们必须添加的额外交易规则：</p><ul><li>如果预测<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>解析为 true，那么从那时起，我们允许交易者将<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>替换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span>出现在逻辑表达式中的任何位置。类似地，如果它解析为 false，我们随后允许用<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>替换<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。这可以被认为是等价交换的一个特例。与所有其他交易规则一样，该规则是可逆的，尽管使用该特定规则的反向版本没有多大意义。</li></ul><p>在最简单的情况下，如果事件<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>发生，该规则允许将<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的股份转换为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\top"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊤</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的股份，从而以 1 美元赎回它们。</p><p>应用：条件预测市场。假设您在多个条件预测市场中进行交易，以事件<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>为条件。也许您想对给定<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>的预测<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和给定<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>的预测<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span>下注 100 美元。普通预测市场处理条件预测的方式是，当我们所调节的事件没有发生时，解析为 N/A。当市场解决 N/A 时，这意味着所有交易者都会收回投资的资金。因此，如果我在一个普通的预测市场（比如<a href="https://manifold.markets/">Manifold</a> ）上下注，我就必须投入 200 美元的资金来进行下注。尽管这两个市场中只有一个能够最终解决。另一个只会再给我 100 美元。</p><p>直观上看，做这些赌注似乎只需要 100 美元的资本，因为<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>是互斥的，无论两者中的哪一个恰好为真，我都只需要投资 100 美元。如果您曾经在条件预测市场下注，您可能希望能够在条件的两侧进行投资，而无需将所需资本不必要地加倍。具有逻辑份额分割的市场允许这样做。</p><p>条件预测市场使用此规则集的方式如下：为了对<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">给</span></span></span></span></span></span>定的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>下注，我购买<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股票。但我不会用美元购买它们。用美元购买只意味着我投资于<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>本身。相反，我用<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股票购买它们。必须存在某种现行汇率，其他交易者愿意以<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q 的</span></span></span></span></span></span>股份换取<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>的股份，而正是这个汇率给出了<em>有条件的</em>市场价格。现在进行投资，我不需要 200 美元。相反，我可以花费 100 美元铸造 100 股<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>和 100 股<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。然后我可以用我的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>股投资<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，用我的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>股投资<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B\land \neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q。</span></span></span></span></span></span>请注意，如果我只是为了<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">ØQ</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">而</span></span></span></span></span></span>持有我的股票而不是进行投资，那么我们就回到了 Robin Hanson 对条件投资的最初表述：如果<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="Q"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span></span></span></span></span>没有发生，我会收回我的投资。</p><h3>补贴市场</h3><p>在上面的例子中，Alice 和 Bob 被迫证明<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="B"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span></span></span></span></span> ，因为它的股票价格只有 0.6 美元，尽管它是可证明的。众所周知，为了运行预测市场，必须对其进行补贴，即命题中的价格与其否定的总和略低于 1 美元。否则，市场交易就是一场零和游戏，参与者平均没有理由参与。因此，想要知道特定问题答案的人有理由补贴该问题的市场。</p><p>但等一下：假设我们对<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A 的</span></span></span></span></span></span>市场进行补贴，以便<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>的价格总计为 0.99 美元，而不是 1 美元。这允许套利：以 0.99 美元的价格从补贴者处购买<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg A"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A 的</span></span></span></span></span></span>股票，然后进行连接以获取 1 美元，利润为 0.01 美元。这不是我们想要的，我们基本上只是免费赠送几分钱。作为补贴者，我们可以接受在交易中亏损，但我们希望这些钱最终停留在股票上，而这些股票只有通过实际证明我们感兴趣的主张才能赎回。如果交易者可以通过以下方式立即获利只是取消他们之间的所有份额，这并不能实现我们的目标。</p><p>我们也许可以通过讨论证明而不是直接讨论命题来解决这个问题。换句话说，我们可以通过分别补贴<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>和<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box \neg R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>的份额来要求证明或反驳黎曼假设。这些并不是彼此的否定，因此无法抵消。市场机制只是拍卖了一堆<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>股，而没有进行平衡<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\neg \Box R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>股。而这些被拍卖的股票只有证明黎曼假设才能赎回。或者，至少通过证明黎曼假设有一个证明。有人可能会找到<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>的非构造性证明，尽管系统外的人类观察者可能会决定他们愿意扩展他们的公理，以便<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="\Box R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-ams-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">□</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>的此类非构造性证明本身也算作证明的<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。</p><h3>附录：完整性</h3><p>事实证明，这些交易法则是完整的，因为它们允许将任何一组股票转换为任何其他同等价值的股票。等值意味着两组股票可以以相同金额赎回，无论所有基本主张如何解决。 （这里的设置是，我们有一些基本<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A, B, C, ..."><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">命题</span></span><span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">，</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">，</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">......</span></span></span></span></span></span>每个都可以是真或假。这些可以是预测市场预测，或者（尽管这里的数学有点糟糕-定义）它们可能是尚未证明或反驳的命题。）</p><p>为了便于理解，我通过例子给出一个“证明”。假设<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="X"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.024em;">X</span></span></span></span></span></span>是命题<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A, B, C"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span></span></span></span></span>的某种表达式。然后我们可以用析取范式来表达它。假设结果为： <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="X = (A\land B\land C)\lor (A\land B\land \neg C)\lor (\neg A\land \neg B\land C)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.024em;">X</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。简而言之，我们定义<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="A\land B\land C = P; A\land B\land \neg C = Q; \neg A\land \neg B\land C = R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">；</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.151em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">；</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">A</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">Ø</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">B</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.045em;">C</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>使得<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="X = P\lor Q\lor R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.024em;">X</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.077em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">=</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space3"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span> 。我们将表达式<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P, Q, R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">、</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>称为“one-hot”表达式，因为它们对于其中一种可能结果都是正确的。我们可以将<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="X"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.024em;">X</span></span></span></span></span></span>中的份额转换为基础 one-hot 表达式中的份额，如下所示：</p><p> <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P\lor Q\lor R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>从<span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="X"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.024em;">X</span></span></span></span></span></span>开始</p><p><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P\lor Q\lor R, \bot"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.372em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">⊥</span></span></span></span></span></span>买假免费</p><p><span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P\lor Q\lor R, P\land (Q\lor R)"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∧</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">(</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.593em;">)</span></span></span></span></span></span>等价交换（不同one-hot表达式是矛盾的）</p><p> <span class="mjpage"><span class="mjx-chtml"><span class="mjx-math" aria-label="P, Q\lor R"><span class="mjx-mrow" aria-hidden="true"><span class="mjx-mi"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em; padding-right: 0.109em;">P</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="margin-top: -0.144em; padding-bottom: 0.519em;">,</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space1"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.519em; padding-bottom: 0.446em;">Q</span></span> <span class="mjx-mo MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-main-R" style="padding-top: 0.298em; padding-bottom: 0.372em;">∨</span></span> <span class="mjx-mi MJXc-space2"><span class="mjx-char MJXc-TeX-math-I" style="padding-top: 0.446em; padding-bottom: 0.298em;">R</span></span></span></span></span></span>逻辑份额分割</p><p>我们可以重复这个过程，直到我们在每个单独的 one-hot 表达式中都拥有份额。</p><p> <span class="mjpage"><span class="mj